org.apache.flex.abc.graph.algorithms

Class DominatorTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.abc.graph.algorithms.DominatorTree

  • public class DominatorTree
extends Object
    An implementation of the O(n log n) Lengauer-Tarjan algorithm for building the dominator tree of a flowgraph.
